title: Community Economic Development Committee 9/21/21
description:
In-person attendance is currently prohibited per Washington State Governor's Proclamation 20-28.15., until the COVID-19 State of Emergency is terminated or Proclamation 20-28 is rescinded by the Governor or State legislature. Meeting participation is limited to access by telephone conference line and online by the Seattle Channel.


Agenda: Call to Order; Approval of the Agenda; Public Comment; Office of Planning and Community Development: Equitable Development Initiative Update; Reappointments to Seattle Women's Commission; Office of Arts and Culture: Race and Social Justice Report 2021; CB 120162: establishing a new 15th Avenue East Business Improvement Area (BIA); CB 120180: relating to human rights.
